(112, 2, 'on', 'File Share', '', '', '', '', 'Music for the Bell', '<p>Here is original music written by a fellow PAVCS member, Seth Gray, for us to use at our discretion.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To save the music in Internet Explorer</strong>: Right-click on the links below, and select \\"Save Target As...\\" in the context menu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To save the music in FireFox</strong>: Right click on the links below, and select \\"Save Link As...\\" in the context menu.</p>\r\n<p>If you are having trouble, then it might be easier from here: <a href=\\"http://www.box.net/shared/93r2kn0yq6\\" target=\\"_blank\\">http://www.box.net/shared/93r2kn0yq6</a>.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 'a:1:{s:25:"m07k57qrd3qls4u16an6tgq6g";s:5:"Music";}', '', '', '', '', ''),
(125, 1, 'on', 'Forum', '', '', '', '', 'Questions', '<p>If you came across any questions while writing or posting your article, submit them here:</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'a:24:{i:0;s:3:"222";i:1;s:3:"227";i:2;s:3:"222";i:3;s:3:"245";i:4;s:3:"272";i:5;s:3:"247";i:6;s:3:"264";i:7;s:3:"269";i:8;s:3:"268";i:9;s:3:"251";i:10;s:3:"250";i:11;s:3:"260";i:12;s:3:"272";i:13;s:3:"272";i:14;s:3:"250";i:15;s:3:"272";i:16;s:3:"272";i:17;s:3:"250";i:18;s:3:"272";i:19;s:3:"272";i:20;s:3:"272";i:21;s:3:"272";i:22;s:3:"250";i:23;s:3:"277";}', 'a:24:{i:0;i:1314713958;i:1;i:1315941979;i:2;i:1317833498;i:3;i:1317843694;i:4;i:1317909983;i:5;i:1317918235;i:6;i:1317919365;i:7;i:1317939788;i:8;i:1317996139;i:9;i:1318000961;i:10;i:1318007854;i:11;i:1318256795;i:12;i:1318348351;i:13;i:1318357172;i:14;i:1318421471;i:15;i:1318423692;i:16;i:1318423818;i:17;i:1318442799;i:18;i:1319054203;i:19;i:1319055019;i:20;i:1319055280;i:21;i:1319056790;i:22;i:1323789318;i:23;i:1331217000;}', 'a:24:{i:0;s:156:"<p><span style=\\"background-color: #000000; color: #00ffff;\\">Hi everyone! When is our first issue and meeting and all that good stuff to happen?</span></p>";i:1;s:76:"<p>Hi everyone! When is our meeting this year? I can\\''t seem to find it!</p>";i:2;s:86:"<p><span style=\\"background-color: #000000; color: #00ffff;\\">Hi everyone!!</span></p>";i:3;s:33:"<p>@ Samantha, today at 3:15.</p>";i:4;s:26:"<p>Hey everybody!!! :)</p>";i:5;s:53:"<p>Ooooh, looks like Tuesday is winning so far...</p>";i:6;s:21:"<p>Hi everyone!:)</p>";i:7;s:142:"I look forward to working together with everyone and making sure that we will have a lot of fun and victories. Anyway, good luck to everyone. ";i:8;s:57:"<p>Hi Everybody!</p>\r\n<p>This should be a fun course.</p>";i:9;s:41:"<p>Hey every1 whatz up? --the sky-lol</p>";i:10;s:116:"<p>sup ppl.&nbsp; just so u know, SuperTrance (the song down there) is my song I made.&nbsp; Just to let u know.</p>";i:11;s:22:"<p>Hi everyone! :D</p>";i:12;s:77:"<p>Hey folks just soo u know The song I Want to live a life is by me.. :)</p>";i:13;s:51:"<p>Check Out \\"I want 2 live a life\\" (new!!!!)</p>";i:14;s:64:"<p>that song sounds familiar....are u in maddix\\''s homeroom?</p>";i:15;s:75:"<p>yep...... I played the other version of the song in her homeroom. :)</p>";i:16;s:52:"<p>This one is the newer version.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>";i:17;s:101:"<p>cool. then&nbsp;u remember supertrance?&nbsp; the trance/electronic song i played in homeroom?</p>";i:18;s:52:"<p>who posted the song \\"Daddy got leggies 2 ?\\"</p>";i:19;s:77:"<p>The song \\"so beautiful\\" is by me. It doesn\\''t have the words though.</p>";i:20;s:55:"<p>it has words but its not recorded with that one.</p>";i:21;s:142:"<p>\\"Daddy Got leggies 2\\" is by joel Tuck and his two brothers.</p>\r\n<p>Drums:Joel Tuck</p>\r\n<p>Piano:Jeremy Tuck</p>\r\n<p>Bass:Jared Tuck</p>";i:22;s:38:"<p>maelstrom of madness is my song</p>";i:23;s:13:"<p>Hello!</p>";}'),
